Comment: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:11.09,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Why are you crying
Comment: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:17.08,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,When I'm not even crying?
Comment: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:23.16,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,When your pain is so much more severe
Comment: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:30.65,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,And I can't tell who's worse off
Comment: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:38.41,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Even the worst of days
Comment: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:45.49,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Become precious when I'm with you
