Comment: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:53.93,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,So if there's anything I can do for you,
Comment: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:58.77,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Just let me know
Comment: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:10.41,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,I want to see you happy, forever and always
Comment: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.43,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,You're just like a sunflower—
Comment: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:23.08,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Your kindness is striking, and your warmth is everything
Comment: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:29.17,ED3E,,0,0,0,karaoke,I want you to know this from here on out,
